  <?dbhtml dir="picker"?>
  <title>iOS toolkit picker</title>
  <para>
  	A <emphasis>picker</emphasis> lets the user choose between certain options by spinning a wheel on the screen. Picker views
  	allow users to quickly choose between a set of distinct options.   
  </para>
  <para role="tip">
  	Please keep in mind that it is not possible to object map single columns within the picker but to object map the picker 
  	as a whole only. In order to interact with single columns you have to use the according actions. 
  </para>
